HEADWORD: Ovotesttis
<hw>O`vo*test"tis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Ovum</er>, and <er>Testis</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
organ which produces both ova and spermatozoids; an hermaphrodite
gland.</def>⟦br⟧
